<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About — Snap & Snack</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Hey I'm Aswin — a traveller who eats first and asks questions later. Read my story.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:title" content="About Anish — Snap & Snack">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Hey I'm Anish — a traveller who eats first and asks questions later.">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://snapandsnack-production.up.railway.app/about">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <!-- Google Analytics -->

  <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-N9JTYL4795"></script>

  <script>

    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];

    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}

    gtag('js', new Date());

    gtag('config', 'G-N9JTYL4795');

  </script>


</head>
<body>

  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="container nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Snap &amp; <span>Snack</span></a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
        <a href="/gallery">Gallery</a>
        <a href="/about" class="active">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        <div class="toggle-track" id="dark-toggle" onclick="toggleDark()" title="Toggle dark mode">
  <div class="toggle-thumb" id="toggle-thumb">☀️</div>
</div>
</div>
      </div>
      <button class="nav-hamburger" onclick="toggleMenu()">☰</button>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-mobile" id="nav-mobile">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
      <a href="/gallery">Gallery</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      <<div class="toggle-track" id="dark-toggle" onclick="toggleDark()" title="Toggle dark mode">
  <div class="toggle-thumb" id="toggle-thumb">☀️</div>
</div>
</div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container-sm">

    <div class="about-page-header">
      <img src="/me.jpg" alt="Anish" class="about-page-avatar" style="object-fit:cover">
      <h1>Hey, I'm NonChalant!</h1>
      <p class="about-page-sub">Traveller · Food lover · Photographer</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-page-body">

      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>My story</h2>
        <p>I'm a traveller who believes the best way to understand a place is through its food. I pick up my camera, hop on a plane (or a bus, or a tuk-tuk), and go looking for the real story behind every destination.</p>
        <p>This blog started as a personal diary and turned into something I actually share with the world. Every post here is a real experience — no filters, no pretending everything was perfect.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>What I do</h2>
        <div class="about-cards">
          <div class="about-feat">
            <span>✈️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Travel</strong>
              <p>I go wherever curiosity takes me — mountains, cities, beaches, street markets.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-feat">
            <span>🍜</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Eat everything</strong>
              <p>Street food, local spots, hole-in-the-wall places. If locals eat there, I'm in.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-feat">
            <span>📷</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Photograph moments</strong>
              <p>I try to capture the feeling of a place, not just how it looks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-feat">
            <span>✍️</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Write honestly</strong>
              <p>Real stories — what went wrong, what surprised me, what I'd do again.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>Why Snap & Snack?</h2>
        <p>Because every trip has two things in common — I always have my camera, and I'm always hungry. The name felt right the moment I thought of it. 😄</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>Get in touch</h2>
        <p>Have a question, a recommendation, or just want to say hi? I'd love to hear from you!</p>
        <div style="margin-top:1rem;display:flex;gap:0.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <a href="/blog" class="read-btn">Read my posts →</a>
          <a href="/gallery" class="btn btn-outline">See my photos</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Back to top -->
  <button class="back-to-top" id="back-to-top" onclick="scrollToTop()" title="Back to top">↑</button>
  <!-- Dark mode toggle -->
  

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-bottom">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Snap & Snack</div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    function toggleMenu() { document.getElementById('nav-mobile').classList.toggle('open'); }
    window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
      document.getElementById('back-to-top').classList.toggle('visible', window.scrollY > 300);
    });
    function scrollToTop() { window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' }); }
    function toggleDark() {
  const isDark = document.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark');
  localStorage.setItem('darkMode', isDark);
  document.getElementById('dark-toggle').classList.toggle('on', isDark);
  document.getElementById('toggle-thumb').textContent = isDark ? '🌙' : '☀️';
}
if (localStorage.getItem('darkMode') === 'true') {
  document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
  document.getElementById('dark-toggle').classList.add('on');
  document.getElementById('toggle-thumb').textContent = '🌙';
}
  </script>

</body>
</html>
